import React, { useContext, useEffect, useState } from 'react'; import axios from 'axios'; import { UserContext } from '../../App'; const Home=()=>{ const[data,setData]=useState([]); const {state,dispatch}= useContext(UserContext); //fuctionality to fetch the data useEffect(()=>{ //Fetch the data from post db axios.get("http://localhost:5000/allpost",{ headers:{ "Content-Type":"Application/json", "Authorization":"Bearer "+localStorage.getItem("jwt") } }).then(response =>{ console.log(response.data.posts); setData(response.data.posts) }).catch(error=>{ console.log(error); }) },[]) return(
